Program: The Documentary
Title: Episode 1 - Nepal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00f6s9g
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 21 Mar 2011
Far from being in decline, as western newspaper headlines suggest, the nuclear family is emerging as the successful model across much of the developing world. Sociologists say it's now taking root in all but a handful of countries. But what makes it such an irresistible model for the 21st Century? Show less